<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Portfolio</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="loading" class="loading-screen">
    <div class="bounce">
      <i data-lucide="code-2" class="loading-icon"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="loading-text">Loading...</div>
  </div>

  <div class="app">
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="navbar-container">
        <div class="navbar-left">
          <span class="logo">Portfolio</span>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-right">
          <button id="theme-toggle" class="theme-button" aria-label="Toggle theme">
            <i data-lucide="moon"></i>
          </button>
          <a href="https://github.com/YanRapzyy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
            <i data-lucide="github"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@YannRDev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
            <i data-lucide="youtube"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="https://linktr.ee/YannXzz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
            <i data-lucide="message-circle"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
      <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="section-container">
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in">About Me</h2>
          <div class="about-card slide-up">
            <div class="profile-image">
              <img src="https://files.catbox.moe/kdljdi.jpg" alt="Profile">
            </div>
            <p class="about-text">
              Hallo selamat datang di website saya, perkenalkan nama saya "YannRyz Takeshi" website ini sekedar untuk membagi informasi tentang coding, tech, IT, saya hanya pemulah yang diam menyusun logika bergerak error semua.
            </p>
            <div class="skills-tags">
              <span class="tag">JavaScript</span>
              <span class="tag">Ganteng</span>
              <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="skills" class="section">
        <div class="section-container">
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Skills</h2>
          <div class="skills-grid">
            <div class="skill-card slide-up">
              <h3>Frontend</h3>
              <ul class="skill-list">
                <li>HTML</li>
                <li>CSS</li>
                <li>JavaScript</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-card slide-up" style="animation-delay: 200ms">
              <h3>Backend</h3>
              <ul class="skill-list">
                <li>Node.js</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-card slide-up" style="animation-delay: 400ms">
              <h3>Tools</h3>
              <ul class="skill-list">
                <li>VS Code</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <footer class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2024 YannTakeshi. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
